<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>Simple sales</title>
    <meta content="Dave Proffitt" name="author">
    <link href="css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="header"> <img id="logo" src="Logo.gif" alt="ProffittCenter logo"
        title="ProffittCenter logo" style="width: 124px; height: 124px;"
        checked="true">Simple sales</div>
    <p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts18">For normal sales operations:</span></p>
    <p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts9">Type or scan the product code
        followed by the Tab or Enter key (a laser scanner can
        automatically append a tab to scanned bar codes when correctly
        set up). [Unknown products will need to be scanned twice to
        avoid accepting fragments of bar codes as product IDs. After the
        second entry, the label next to the entry box will change to
        'Enter description...' &nbsp;Type this in and press Enter, then
        type in the retail price in pence followed by Enter]</span></p>
    <p class="rvps1"><span class="rvts18">Or</span></p>
    <p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts9">Type the letter </span><span class="rvts12">a</span><span
        class="rvts9"> followed by the Tab or Enter key, or for multiple
        products, type the letter </span><span class="rvts12">a</span><span
        class="rvts9"> &nbsp;followed by the number to be sold and then
        the Tab or Enter key</span></p>
    <p class="rvps1"><span class="rvts18">Or</span></p>
    <p class="rvps5"><span class="rvts9">Type any three or more letters
        â€“ a list of product descriptions will appear in the </span><a class="rvts16"
        href="Alphalookup.html">Alpha lookup</a><span class="rvts9">
        screen, containing words starting with these letters, any one of
        which can be selected with a left click of the mouse or using
        the up and down arrow keys followed by the </span><span class="rvts12">Enter</span><span
        class="rvts9"> key. There are also a set of digits, 0 to 9
        alongside the first ten entries. One of these digits can be
        pressed to select that line. The word entered does not have to
        be the first word of the description. For instance, typing the
        letters &nbsp;</span><span class="rvts12">b l e </span><span class="rvts9">might
        produce a list including an entry for</span><span class="rvts12">
        Domestos </span><span class="rvts17">Ble</span><span class="rvts12">ach
        1l</span></p>
    <p class="rvps6"><span class="rvts18">Or</span></p>
    <p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts9">Type </span><span class="rvts12">10000</span><span
        class="rvts9"> followed by a four digit </span><a class="rvts16"
        href="10000codes.html">10000 code</a><span class="rvts9"> to
        sell items identified by a four digit code applied with a
        pricing gun.</span></p>
    <p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts9"> </span></p>
    <p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts9">The last product sold can be </span><span
        class="rvts12">deleted</span><span class="rvts9"> by pressing
        the </span><span class="rvts12">Delete</span><span class="rvts9">
        key.</span></p>
    <p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts9">To delete the sale of a product
        that is not the last item on the sales screen, first select the
        item by the use of the up and down arrow keys, or by using a
        mouse, and then pressing the </span><span class="rvts12">Delete</span><span
        class="rvts9"> key. </span></p>
    <p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts9">To delete all the items of a
        sale (multiple lines) hold the </span><span class="rvts12">Shift</span><span
        class="rvts9"> key down whilst pressing </span><span class="rvts12">Delete</span><span
        class="rvts9">.</span></p>
    <p class="rvps3"><span class="rvts18">Price and weight encoding</span></p>
    <p class="rvps3"><a class="rvts16" href="Priceandweightencoding.html">Price

        and weight encoded</a><span class="rvts9"> products are handled
        correctly, but new products cannot be handled in the sales
        screen..</span></p>
    <p></p>
  </body>
</html>
